{"tid":2426982,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"有人好有心整理咗今日各義士被捕前嘅說話","createTime":"2021-02-28T12:42:47.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T17:46:18.000Z","uid":74339,"like":67,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"3d679295a816c0e7f06c020739561bb2e3155d2f","tid":2426982,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:42:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/704949632/posts/10158322302609633/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F704949632%2Fposts%2F10158322302609633%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=5f92e0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/704949632/posts/10158322302609633/?d=n</a><br />\n<br />\n想把看到他們對大家說的話抄一點出來。溫柔堅強的人們。可以的話，明天到西九龍裁判法院聲援吧。<br />\n<br />\n🙏<br />\n<br />\n朱凱廸<br />\n<br />\n「感謝香港人過去十五年給我貢獻社會的機會，今天為了我們共同的理想負罪，深感光榮。大家的問候都收到了，我祝福大家每天活得充實，無論在什麼處境，都令身邊人感到愛與希望。」<br />\n<br />\n鄒家成<br />\n<br />\n當苦難看似無盡地持續下去，我們需要的不是更多對苦難的想像，而是超越苦難的希望和決心。苦難使人成長，希望使人強大。漫長的黑暗歲月，不論大家流落何方、在街頭、在獄中、在地方、在海外，我們都需要無盡的希望，方能支撐我們一同奮鬥下去。<br />\n<br />\n擁抱希望不代表天真或自欺欺人，而是對自己信念的肯定。即刻此刻我們與政權之間的力量非常懸殊，但只要我們都願意保持耐性，繼續做應該要做的事，我始終相信屬於我們的時代終將降臨。但在那之前，我們必先將「苦難的共同體」進化成「希望的共同體」，大家懷抱住共同的希望，一步一步踏實地走下去。<br />\n<br />\n岑敖暉<br />\n<br />\n毋須懷憂喪志<br />\n條路係我地自己揀<br />\n係成個香港一齊揀<br />\n揀左，就要繼續行落去。<br />\n歷史沒有回頭路，只有身前身。<br />\n<br />\n袁嘉蔚<br />\n<br />\n團圓，在今日的香港不容易，好好生活，爭取最多人的重聚。香港人，撐住。<br />\n謝謝大家的問好，但你們認識的袁嘉蔚心臟可強大的，不用太擔心啦嘿。<br />\n今晚一起吃湯圓吧❤️<br />\n<br />\n梁晃維<br />\n<br />\n「希望大家記得當初行出嚟嘅原因。」<br />\n<br />\n鄭達鴻<br />\n<br />\n「盡力呼吸，好好過活，不是失去對生命的期望」。<br />\n<br />\n趙家賢<br />\n<br />\n「為咗我哋所愛嘅香港好好活下去，加油」<br />\n<br />\n區諾軒<br />\n<br />\n胸を張って生きろ<br />\n<br />\n林景楠<br />\n<br />\n「香港人加油！」<br />\n<br />\n何桂藍<br />\n<br />\n比起平安，我更希望尋求的是心安，而兩者有時相反。祝願各位，能夠覓得心安之途，然後，一往無前。<br />\n<br />\n毛孟靜<br />\n<br />\n即使世道未慣，我心到處悠然<br />\n#香港人總是愛香港 ~<br />\nI maybe physically feeble, but I&rsquo;m mentally sturdy<br />\nNo worries<br />\nWe all love Hong Kong yah ~<br />\n<br />\n楊雪盈<br />\n<br />\n「事情來得急，非常感激各方好友迅速支援。今日我有帶兩隻貓在身（一團貓毛），好平靜，大家請放心，我有足夠勇氣去面對。」<br />\n<br />\n馮達浚<br />\n<br />\n心境澄明，自有公論。<br />\n在艱彌厲，戰鬥到底。<br />\n我不恐懼自身之事，<br />\n我只恐懼無後來者。<br />\n<br />\n梁國雄<br />\n<br />\n「國安法無法無天、釋放所有政治犯」<br />\n<br />\n張可森<br />\n<br />\nIdeas are bulletproof.<br />\nOur future is never determined.<br />\nIt&rsquo;s the people who can walk through the fog,<br />\nthat can actualise the future.<br />\nOur will and our faith will be the light guiding us through everything.<br />\n<br />\n黃子悅<br />\n<br />\n山中人自正，路險心亦平。感謝大家的關心，假如真的還押，希望當我出來的時候，大家還在，還在堅持著。<br />\n<br />\n尹兆堅<br />\n<br />\n直至現時，我堅信自己無做過違反國安法嘅事。我從政生涯中，我都無做過違反香港法律嘅事。一直本著為公眾利益，服務巿民態度做事。<br />\n<br />\n我無畏無懼、迎難而上，希望表現出奔風知勁草，大家要做返個人，做返自己！要記住自己初心！無論受到任何打壓，都要保重，平安！<br />\n<br />\n郭家麒<br />\n<br />\n面對不斷的打壓，步入政治寒冬，我們唯有靠彼此支持、互相照應，在患難中艱苦奮進，監獄能將我們隔絕，但不能阻止我們心靈相通、彼此照應；鐵鏈能鎖住我們的身體，但鎖不住我們的思想和靈魂！<br />\n<br />\nStay calm and carry on.This too shall pass!謹記不是見到希望才堅持，是堅持才有希望！大家保重！<br />\n<br />\n吳敏兒<br />\n<br />\n放棄只需一秒，堅持卻需要要一世<br />\n<br />\n到秀茂坪警署報到，預備好最壞的應對，堅持心中所想，工會加油，香港人加油。<br />\n<br />\n陳志全<br />\n<br />\n不要抱著「赴刑場等殺頭的心態面對政權的清算，只要一息尚存，就有機會捲土重來。<br />\n<br />\n呂智恆<br />\n<br />\n好開心認識到咁多位手足，我一定會想起你哋：）<br />\n<br />\n希望大家好好活下去 願平安<br />\n<br />\n那美好的仗我已經打過了，當跑的路我已經跑盡了，該信的道我已經守住了。（提摩太後書4：7）<br />\n<br />\n王百羽<br />\n<br />\n大家唔需要傷春悲秋<br />\n香港人要行嘅路點都要行落去<br />\n做一個好的人，阻止錯的事，為未來做對的事<br />\n<br />\n李予信<br />\n<br />\n無論面對怎樣的荒謬，香港人也要好好生活，活在真實之中<br />\n我以當香港人的議員為榮，無怨無悔。<br />\n<br />\n余慧明<br />\n<br />\n與其悲觀地過<br />\n倒不如笑著迎接未知<br />\n<br />\n如果不幸無法短期內再會面<br />\n只想大家記住成立工會嘅初衷<br />\n繼續堅持自己做對的事<br />\n就夠了<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/704949632/posts/10158322302609633/?d=n\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F704949632%2Fposts%2F10158322302609633%2F%3Fd%3Dn&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=5f92e0b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/704949632/posts/10158322302609633/?d=n</a>"},{"pid":"6ea98ea182ceb6503efca62990102d42e841ec4c","tid":2426982,"uid":277888,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:54:15.000Z","msg":"祝你在亂流下平安 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a52655837be0bd430c01ed2903377fc756ee3eb","tid":2426982,"uid":26014,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:55:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25ae37639468a9460889c4c858aacf04d489ce8e","tid":2426982,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:55:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"510088421837d06720f425be4650351d774337cd","tid":2426982,"uid":321895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:55:17.000Z","msg":"推二"},{"pid":"6facd51eeaf83025589cab541ced0544ae87e8e0","tid":2426982,"uid":70964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:56:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"5c343d6ce9e21c7f94a0ef15e7415a71e57dcd33","tid":2426982,"uid":268217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T12:58:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/sneeze.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0401e50b8fbe58ffbf0b52c48854a396bb9ab8d","tid":2426982,"uid":74339,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"我對依句特別感觸。義士們怕嘅唔係被捕，而係後繼無人<br />\n<br />\n馮達浚<br />\n<br />\n「心境澄明，自有公論。<br />\n在艱彌厲，戰鬥到底。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我不恐懼自身之事，<br />\n我只恐懼無後來者。</span>」"},{"pid":"45d1eeb7eb95a3f9ecc48a4bd2ef9d7add68d463","tid":2426982,"uid":204670,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:28:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"7ccadca971a1c42b2604b0d7aad660db78719ea6","tid":2426982,"uid":74339,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d0401e50b8fbe58ffbf0b52c48854a396bb9ab8d","tid":2426982,"uid":74339,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:27:47.000Z","msg":"我對依句特別感觸。義士們怕嘅唔係被捕，而係後繼無人<br />\n<br />\n馮達浚<br />\n<br />\n「心境澄明，自有公論。<br />\n在艱彌厲，戰鬥到底。<br />\n<span class=\"red\">我不恐懼自身之事，<br />\n我只恐懼無後來者。</span>」"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:33:27.000Z","msg":"應該話<span class=\"red\">最怕</span>嘅唔係被捕"},{"pid":"8a7a523d3a7ba62c203275dab06dea19eba5c09f","tid":2426982,"uid":185628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:40:57.000Z","msg":"Oliver Queen<br />\nYou have failed this city!"},{"pid":"3e97930e27c42a54827fd06b99fea29ead6340b7","tid":2426982,"uid":104917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"英文version<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/eliotchen97/status/1365969424147222534?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feliotchen97%2Fstatus%2F1365969424147222534%3Fs%3D21&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=b105e869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feliotchen97%2Fstatus%2F1365969424147222534%3Fs%3D21&h=e9622ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/eliotchen97/status/1365969424147222534?s=21</a>"},{"pid":"5329264ac8a051cdbe721414b3230cd40a5810d6","tid":2426982,"uid":67424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:51:14.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"34cb75f8f9db8a95b0dd28843792b28b0fc6f36f","tid":2426982,"uid":27909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:52:12.000Z","msg":"天佑義士"},{"pid":"19ffa098e2deae982abb4c6b35b8ec0bb10281ed","tid":2426982,"uid":233325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:53:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3357a8c21b961c22110b46a098d52162e42b2f96","tid":2426982,"uid":56248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:54:26.000Z","msg":"睇到想喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9312d57e36380b05e60bbdb0093b9a826e35dc7","tid":2426982,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:56:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3dafb2195fde9a111b049e0608dbee759d8c3c94","tid":2426982,"uid":92442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:57:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"959d4c9a924b54e59c208718da7f1b243e15f67a","tid":2426982,"uid":91721,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:11:32.000Z","msg":"up"},{"pid":"233b5627252d05f290b27495dd86354613f689de","tid":2426982,"uid":605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:12:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44b64d375b95cf6d4789b03e426aaa7af66061f9","tid":2426982,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:32:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b189886c4e1bf5be9740376fb50c707ee2864e5","tid":2426982,"uid":43062,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:32:45.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d48c868fb8128aa987b2881d351c6c888681c9c6","tid":2426982,"uid":9193,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:36:02.000Z","msg":"雪盈bb<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c02f077a95033ec88f05b53f9afd5dc87fca376a","tid":2426982,"uid":74339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd8eb80d0fabfa8b7d6cab45e33334cf091b0f6c","tid":2426982,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T14:52:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}],"pinned":{"pid":"3e97930e27c42a54827fd06b99fea29ead6340b7","tid":2426982,"uid":104917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T13:47:35.000Z","msg":"英文version<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://twitter.com/eliotchen97/status/1365969424147222534?s=21\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feliotchen97%2Fstatus%2F1365969424147222534%3Fs%3D21&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3gwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=b105e869\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Feliotchen97%2Fstatus%2F1365969424147222534%3Fs%3D21&h=e9622ebc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://twitter.com/eliotchen97/status/1365969424147222534?s=21</a>"}}